profile_positions.description:
Via "SteVesta" I helped organizations with my knowledge by guiding construction and real estate projects in the right direction, so that the optimum result can be achieved. Activities: 
- development management from feasibility study to realization; 
- selecting / contracting / directing advisers, contractors and other parties; 
- leading multidisciplinary development teams, construction teams, real estate processes
- strategic real estate management / transaction management / valuation of RE; 
- consultant contract matters and tender management; 
- building economic advice / investment analyzes / claim scans.
